               example, we're checking out foo/bar/baz from the
               repository:

	       1) create foo, point CVS/Repository to <root>/foo
	       2)     .. foo/bar                   .. <root>/foo/bar
	       3)     .. foo/bar/baz               .. <root>/foo/bar/baz
	       
